":{"pid":"dd2aea278a38f78eec0cbd1a7bb09164b9b4620f","tid":1810184,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n出多次兵香港<br />\n不過唔係侵略<br />\n係救援<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:04:05.000Z","msg":"有啲人話日本人都好多日豬<br />\n但老實講關注咗香港7個月都仲當2020年係news of the world<br />\n<br />\n真係好少見"},{"pid":"c9caa3fb29827766b6dddf06c3b12e781f81a7ea","tid":1810184,"uid":221265,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:06:26.000Z","msg":"睇下周庭點講<br />\n<br />\n池上彰2018年嚟香港時就有訪佢<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CLBtgYg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCLBtgYg.jpg&h=ea16073a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>【與池上彰先生見面】</strong><br />\n昨天有幸在香港與池上彰先生一起參與電視節目的錄影，跟他分享了很多香港在主權移交後的種種改變、自由空間的收窄和打壓。<br />\n<strong>池上先生是日本相當有名的記者和節目主持人，經常在節目中就爭議性議題質問日本的國會議員和官員（當然亦包括安倍晉三）。我最難忘的，是他在兩年前訪問當年剛當選議員的SPEED成員今井繪理子，發現她雖是沖繩出身，剛對沖繩問題一無所知、被問得啞口無言。</strong><br />\n能被池上先生面對面訪問，是十分難得的機會，希望今後我們能有機會就中港和日本的問題討論更多！<br />\n（相片中的是池上彰san、本上manami san、吉谷彩子san）<br />\n#第一次搭觀光巴士"},{"pid":"8b0e19dc87da254d76d4fe7821a42189b22a70be","tid":1810184,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:07:37.000Z","msg":"twitter 相<br />\n佢啲書好好賣<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lc0BqSa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLc0BqSa.jpg&h=59d3c18e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e4a2498c8d71eecdaf21d3954138747ef88e4501","tid":1810184,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"982bfdd0443684165f8a288643631fa04777f828","tid":1810184,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2aea278a38f78eec0cbd1a7bb09164b9b4620f","tid":1810184,"uid":343361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-03T16:03:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n